reviewText:
A cheap, enjoyable RPGMaker made experience that can be bought for 5 bucks, or if you wait for a sale, 19 cents!

Pros:
- Easily obtainable achievements;
- Interesting take on the history side!;
- Replayability, due to the existence of 3 different endings;
- Every object has a description!

Cons:
- No voice acting;
- Low resolution, some crashes and freezes;
- Not recommended for gamers that don't enjoy RPGMaker made games.

Not really much to speak of, just ponder your purchase using these aspects :D

PS: Don't blink!
